{
  "stem": "2723.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I would think about 50, 60 people were there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Children and adults.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was difficult because we had restrictions.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For instance, I recall vividly that milk was only available from X to Z.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was, I think, in the span of one hour.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was my duty.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was becoming neurotic and, in fact, became a very nervous child.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because I used to wake up all night thinking, it's time for me to go and get milk.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My mother needed milk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What I didn't tell you was that prior to our going to the ghetto-- from all the stresses and strains, having been to this holding camp, and the stress of treatment that she had to live with-- my mother developed meningitis and was in hospital for many, many weeks.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my sister and I were alone, totally alone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know how we survived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My aunt, of course, helped.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But she was at work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we had to look after our own needs, and shopping, and food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I became very, very locked in on the thought of queuing and going on time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I became neurotic-- really neurotic-- and developed a skin condition, which became a curse to my life, psoriasis, which was strongly linked to that nervous tension.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we didn't go hungry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "When my mother recovered-- and she did, very slowly, with lots of setbacks-- but I do think food, and cooking, and nutrition, and our health was so important to her that her will to be a mother pulled her through.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I remember we had perhaps one-dish meals.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But they were very good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I was a very good eater.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And as long as it filled my stomach, I wasn't very worried.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We really didn't go hungry.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
